THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby extend sincere and heartfelt condolences to the family and friends of Sharon
Courtney and does hereby honor and recognize her remarkable life of service and legacy and
her many contributions to the city of New Orleans and the state of Louisiana.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
family of Sharon Courtney.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
